<P>He next aimed at the crown of France, but at the lo&s;s of a very con&s;iderable trea&s;ure. He was the dupe of the emperor Maximilian, the poore&s;t prince in Europe, and gave him&s;elf up to the guidance of Cardinal Wol&s;ey.</P>
