<PB N="69" REF="74">into Scotland, and after a little oppo&s;ition, Charles <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> obliged to fly, and e&s;caped his pur&s;uers by di&s;gui&s;ing <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">&s;elf in the dre&s;s of a pea&s;ant.</P>
