<PB N="71" REF="76">to William, prince of Orange, who had married <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">es's elde&s;t daughter. He was a prince of great abili|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> and a declared enemy of the papi&s;ts.</P>
