<P>In &s;hort, nothing happens in this world without hi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> order and permi&s;&s;ion. God then di&s;po&s;es all the event<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> of the world. The &s;malle&s;t action of every creature, the lea&s;t thought of the mind, is all regulated by his
