<P>Having now entered, I believe, pretty ful<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> into the heavenly bodies, and into two of the element namely Fire and Air; let me reque&s;t, if I have <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> tired you, to give me &s;ome account of the other t<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> Earth and Water.</P>
