<P>As you &s;eem di&s;po&s;ed at attend, we w<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> from the heavens de&s;cend upon the earth. Here t<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> we are; and as the waters occupy the greate&s;t part the &s;urface of the terre&s;trial globe, we will be with con&s;idering the Sea.</P>
